    "description": "Princess Ruby 是一款 2D 平台游戏，您可以在其中扮演公主在每个关卡中奔跑，以收集被龙从她的城堡中偷走的物品。该游戏是为幼儿设计的，可以在 2 人本地合作中玩，它可能具有挑战性，但控制很简单。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195050/extras/737c30dfa64a9de43226afa940bdcb30.poster.avif?t=1670537080\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195050/extras/737c30dfa64a9de43226afa940bdcb30.webm?t=1670537080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195050/extras/737c30dfa64a9de43226afa940bdcb30.mp4?t=1670537080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >2 玩家本地合作</h2>使用键盘或控制器进出本地合作社。如果你到达下一个检查点，其他玩家可以传送到它，让你帮助新玩家跳过太难的部分。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195050/extras/5e7a546de2568d4cf71fce2ef25903ca.poster.avif?t=1670537080\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195050/extras/5e7a546de2568d4cf71fce2ef25903ca.webm?t=1670537080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195050/extras/5e7a546de2568d4cf71fce2ef25903ca.mp4?t=1670537080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >专为新玩家设计</h2>该游戏一次只能在每只手上使用 1 个按钮，让幼儿或其他刚接触游戏的人更容易玩。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >选择你的挑战</h2>在普通模式下，收集宝石会给你额外的生命，如果你失败了 3 次，金色的心会让你无懈可击。或者选择困难模式进行真正的挑战，每个关卡只需额外增加 1 条生命即可完成，而最后的关卡并不容易！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195050/extras/4a8420229d137a1b2459e2a7a9f87779.poster.avif?t=1670537080\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195050/extras/4a8420229d137a1b2459e2a7a9f87779.webm?t=1670537080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195050/extras/4a8420229d137a1b2459e2a7a9f87779.mp4?t=1670537080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你自己的公主</h2>从各种外观选项中进行选择，并在完成关卡时解锁新服装。<br>让你的公主随心所欲，改变你的外表和服装的颜色。<br>完成关卡后解锁新服装，例如骑士、女牛仔、超级英雄和女巫。如果你能找到它，你甚至可以改变你的独角兽的颜色。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195050/extras/e21fd8ab2a26e32d45dbea6a227879f2.poster.avif?t=1670537080\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195050/extras/e21fd8ab2a26e32d45dbea6a227879f2.webm?t=1670537080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195050/extras/e21fd8ab2a26e32d45dbea6a227879f2.mp4?t=1670537080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >城堡、龙和独角兽</h2>一条龙用它的魔法夺走了你的城堡、玩具、宠物甚至你父母的一切！<br>从每个级别拯救他们，您将能够在玩具屋中心级别与他们一起玩。",
